page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content: The children of classes 6N(Mr.C.North) and 6W(Mrs.J.Williams)of Seal School and class TB(Mrs O.V.Anderson) of Manhood Community College would like to thank all the teachers,children,parents,governors and other people of Selsey who have helped them with this project especially: The Parish Council, Peter Ogden,chairman of the Parish Council.Brian Kennedy who helped to take the photos.,Mr.Halpin,Chairman of the Cricket Club,Cecil French,Crablands Bowling and Tennis Club.Peter Grindley,Club Professional,Selsey Golf Club.Rev.Dowson,Father Cassam,The Tyler family (Evangelical Church) Bob Lord,Pagham Harbour Nature Reserve.Mr.B.Hill,Coastguard.Patrick Moore,astronomer and broadcaster.
